@startuml seq_04_manage_profile
title Sequence Diagram: UC-04 Manage Profile

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "User Controller" as Controller
participant "User Service" as Service
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "User Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Edit profile info & select new avatar
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /api/users/profile (multipart form data)
Controller -> Service: Update Profile
Service -> Repo: Find User by ID
Repo --> Service: User found
Service -> Service: Validate profile fields

alt New avatar/cover image uploaded
    Service -> Cloudinary: Upload image stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: Return Image URL & Public ID
end

Service -> Repo: Update User Profile (including new image URLs if any)
Repo --> Service: Profile updated
Service --> Controller: Updated User Info
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display updated profile
@enduml